    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is increasingly rare in the secondary market. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail has been preserved to an exacting degree. For the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
